<br />

<br />
In your post you mention how eventually you will all have Ebon armour and Adept 3's that are usefull, however, if you add the rare loot in a predictable fashion then that too fits into your statement.
<br />

<br />
I am only speculating, but I think this is an attempt to control the flow of rare items into the world which to me is a good thing.
<br />

<br />
I understand your frustrations, but I think if you look at this in the long run, it is a good thing.
<br />

<br />
It actually sounds to me like there may be to many of these rare resources dropping.
<br />

<br />
I remember back in the old days when a FBSS was something to be proud of, and then there were the days when it sold for 10 plat on 7 afk merchant bots in the Bazaar. This of course may not be the best example but I think it makes my point.
<br />

