          <td colspan="2"><span
class="postbody">Good ideas coming in.   Keep them coming.
<br />

<br />
*semi thread jack*
<br />
An interesting point to make about Metal chest loot is it seems to come from a randomizer off a  "uber loot" table.  We have gotten the same loot from different mobs in these metal chests.  With this in place - there is no specific item you get from said Uber mob and this makes it almost impossible to "Pharm" a specific piece of loot.  
<br />

<br />
Personally I agree with this design.  Instead of killing XYZ mob for a specific loot and knowing it will go to XYZ classes only - there is no predetermination of what class (if not all classes) can use the reward off a 24 person raid mob.  Sure it is annoying at time (wtf 2 med bps...) and random but this serves the whole better than the individual.<br />_________________<br />Noah
<br />
