            Attaching loot to a mob...</span></td>
          <td valign="top" nowrap><a href="posting.php?mode=quote&amp;p=334&amp;sid=2c98f5027e08a090ef3be427292d8c82"><img src="templates/ezHyperShadow/images/lang_english/icon_quote.gif" alt="Reply with quote" title="Reply with quote" border="0" /></a>  
